Title: None of the Above
Plot: Dawson is stunned when Eve presents him with a sneak peak at the PSAT test and everyone is tempted to cheat including Joey, whose scholarship is dependent on her SAT scores, and Andie, who is desperately fighting for acceptance to Harvard. But when the test is stolen, it's Pacey that Dawson accuses since he sees Pacey slipping back to his old ways. Meanwhile, Jack is insistent that the football team is purposely beating him down because he is gay.
GuestStars: Brittany Daniel, Niklaus Lange, Aubrey Dollar, Christy Jo Wilburn, Yolanda Camille Chambers, Genevieve Barker, Kelly Cheston
